Subject: [PATCH v2] tracing: Disable interrupt or preemption before acquiring arch_spinlock_t
Date:   Thu, 22 Sep 2022 09:31:58 -0400
Message-Id: <20220922133158.1731333-1-longman@redhat.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
